Azure Bastion provides secure RDP/SSH connectivity to Azure VMs directly through the Azure Portal without exposing public IPs.

Benefits:

* No public RDP/SSH ports
* Browser-based secure access
* Reduced attack surface

For example, administrators manage VMs securely without opening port 3389.

A real-life use case is secure remote administration.

Another example is compliance-sensitive environments.

Azure Bastion improves VM access security significantly.
